---------------------------------
3. Installation
---------------------------------

To install, untar the built tar file in some location.

% tar -zxvf biopig/target/biopig-core-0.2.0-bin.tar.gz -C /usr/local/
==> produces a directory /usr/local/biopig-0.2.0/

add /usr/local/biopig-0.2.0/lib/biopig-core-0.2.0-job.jar to your PIG_CLASSPATH environment variable and
you are off.

---------------------------------
4. Running apps
---------------------------------

See readme in ./apps (or after installation, in <INSTALLDIR>/apps/README)

